comments: McDermott (SAS) applies a stayed forearm to Allen's (CLE) body and marginal contact occurs as he defends the shot near the rim.
Mobley (CLE) jumps into Murray's (SAS) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) makes contact with the ball while part of the ball is inside the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.
Poeltl (SAS) turns into Stevens' (CLE) body and initiates contact as he defends the shot near the rim.
Murray (SAS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Allen (CLE) during rebounding.

Possession is awarded to San Antonio.  Murray's (SAS) right foot comes down out of bounds while he is still in possession of the ball and before he throws the ball off of Allen (CLE).  Possession should have been awarded to Cleveland.
Mobley (CLE) moves slightly forward towards Johnson's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Walker IV (SAS) pins the ball to his hip and he resumes his dribble.
Markkanen (CLE) brings his arm down and makes contact with Walker IV's (SAS) head as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) and Poeltl (SAS) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Allen (CLE) cleanly deflects the ball away from Poeltl (SAS) during rebounding.
Garland (CLE) moves slightly forward towards Vassell (SAS) and marginal contact occurs as Vassell secures the loose ball.
Garland (CLE) brings part of his hand under the ball when he brings his dribble to a pause.
Bates-Diop (SAS) is moving alongside Stevens' (CLE) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Bates-Diop (SAS) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
Murray (SAS) is bracing for the contact from Stevens (CLE) and releases away from the contact on the perimeter.
Vassell (SAS) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
